♥ bonnie

wow, IV/XX seems to be a big controversy in the scene. people get so worked up, haha.
so today.. in the morning, me and madeline worked out a scheme to end up with us meeting at central p.s. and getting on the bus to go to the east for the day instead of our own schools. it was so much fun! i got to see/hangout with cam, paco, zack, coady, cody, dan doyle, jordan and some more kids. such sweet times. started smoking pot so early in the day, what a good day! we hung out with cam the most.. such a cutie, i love that kid.
aaaaanyways yes, happy IV/XX everyone, and to the kids who don't celebrate/honour it, i hope you guys all have a sweet day.. keep up the good work.
peace!
..thats pretty much all that i have to say. also, 6 days! :]
maybe we'll feel closer after you buy me a pair of shoes and i punch you in the jaw.
